{"tid":1525207,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"法律撚請解答, 對住警犬有冇得合法自衛?","createTime":"2019-08-31T20:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T23:56:43.000Z","uid":55177,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a133edd61a2e3dc743ff76ced1862123993c9493","tid":1525207,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:27:55.000Z","msg":"當警犬濫權濫捕, 隨街打人行使過份武力既時候<br />\n<br />\n市民有冇權反抗同合法自衛呢?  其他市民有冇權上前幫手保護受警犬威脅既人呢? <br />\n<br />\n如果有, 咁點先算合法? 萬一反抗過程中令警犬傷殘需唔需要負上任何法律責任?<br />\n上前幫手有冇咩限制? 可唔可以推開/拉開警犬? <br />\n<br />\n如果冇, 咁係咪姐係話市民只可以單方面接受暴力對待唔可以作出任何反抗?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇律師巴絲打可以解答下??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b99acba784a6bc2bf9902bb5c5ee43c43d63942","tid":1525207,"uid":55177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:36:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f851a6f6d10f4e22302a65591c1e72ca4f76707","tid":1525207,"uid":164127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:37:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dd4c1cd5430b4c4027e11d8c31347db4cc2ad03","tid":1525207,"uid":192817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:38:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2417aed2bde44c5bd4eaf5fdf2576a5ef6bdb66f","tid":1525207,"uid":227174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:39:18.000Z","msg":"冇委任證或編號可以防衛嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dc68d9f2831df9ef562b8eb1074b19c6345729f","tid":1525207,"uid":55177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T20:40:22.000Z","msg":"如果可以合法反抗暴力既, 以後面對警犬就可以有多好多種方法應對,<br />\n而唔係好似依家咁單方面比人打唔還得手"},{"pid":"2884680922529e79e07bc1212aec419df4edc9c7","tid"